sentences.sentence: Diaminopimelic acid pathway is one of the lysine biosynthetic pathways.
sentences.translation: 二氨基庚二酸途径是赖氨酸生物合成途径之一。

sentences.sentence: Two or more biosynthetic pathways may coexist in a single cell.
sentences.translation: 在同一细胞中可能同时存在两条或更多条生物合成途径。

sentences.sentence: Many of the cellular biosynthetic pathways were first elucidated.
sentences.translation: 首次阐明了许多细胞内生物合成的途径。
